    You recognize the briefing structure — he's presenting the indicators without the conclusion, letting you draw it yourself.  An analyst's habit.
}
"Everything we have is secondhand.  A therapist.  A spouse.  An acquaintance we recruited.  The members themselves don't know they're being observed."
He meets your eyes.  "Which is why we need primary observation."
